data.description:
Welcome to this charming oasis nestled in the picturesque neighborhood of Belmar, centrally located with great schools. This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick home has a spacious layout providing several possibilities to suit your family's needs. The formal dining room could be used as a second living area and the 4th bedroom could also be used as an office, craft space or home school room. 
The beautiful hardwood floors and the wood burning fireplace really make this house feel like home. 
The spacious master suite sits at the back of the home with doors onto the patio, 2 large closets and an updated bathroom. 
Your family will enjoy the nice backyard with a patio, the 7-ft fence, storage building and the Class IV roof is an added bonus!
